I’m very disappointed in ETUDE

Beryeong didn’t mention it but #14 Rose Lilac is an Olive Young exclusive; if I want it, I have to buy it there… except Olive Young doesn’t do DDP (Delivery Duty Paid) meaning that as a European citizen, I have to pay custom duties & fees. Before summer 2021 there was a law that exempted small purchases (<22€) from VAT/custom duties/fees, but that law doesn’t exist anymore, so now a $16 lip product turns into a ~$40 lip product (20% tax + $21 application fee) + shipping. Great!

Usually I don’t have any problems since I buy from Korean beauty shops in Europe, but in this case it’s impossible as it’s an Olive Young exclusive. Even though I wanna give them my money, I don’t wanna pay double especially in taxes. 

Damn the color is so pretty too… and I’m winter cool… damn you ETUDE
